{"tid":2102061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"書展關注組稱每年均有百萬讀者入場　建議今年延期舉行","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T11:48:06.000Z","uid":241764,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cef10966589fb5efe1c941d8b88988800fb7d094","tid":2102061,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"今年書展將於下星期三至本月21日舉行，香港書展關注組建議書展延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n由約50個書商組成、涉及200多個書展攤位的書展關注組發表聲明表示，展期將至，各大小書商已進入物流運輸、貨物調動的最後籌備階段。但書商對如期舉辦書展感憂慮，建議政府及主辦書展的貿發局重新考慮，在補助不變下，延後舉辦本年書展。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537006-20200710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537006-20200710.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=ad690d5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537006-20200710.htm&h=d4043af3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537006-20200710.htm</a>"},{"pid":"27adbb047f553757514d7a21eb316a7c372df603","tid":2102061,"uid":57671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:08:06.000Z","msg":"聽日後日記得投票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYaAEA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYaAEA4.jpg&h=f73580f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFBTrf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFBTrf5.jpg&h=5dd3e3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JApxGPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJApxGPq.jpg&h=a84e2f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5KUU9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5KUU9r.jpg&h=59996e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tv5g8ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftv5g8ur.jpg&h=666c3bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"